{"id":232723543,"title":"🐚尋找香味小步驟","content":"Hello 我是艾琳娜\n這是我第一次po文，目前在台灣文創香水公司任職，以後會把大家常見的問題整理成文章分享給你們😀\n\n如何形容記憶中的味道或是自己想找的香水？\n你可以想像這5件事～\n■觸感：柔軟、粗糙、絲綢的、粉粉的﻿\n﻿\n■重量：輕飄的、扎實的、沈重﻿\n﻿\n■顏色：乳白色、透明的、繽紛的﻿\n﻿\n■聲音：輕柔、尖銳、渾厚﻿、又或著是一首歌\n﻿\n■畫面：婚禮、兒時﻿、慶生、森林冒險\n﻿\nEx. 記憶中的白玫瑰花香，摸起來像絲綢般，輕輕的但很大一束，呈現優雅的乳白色，輕柔的嗓音，好像婚禮上的新娘👰🏻\nhttps://i.imgur.com/qm9SIcR.jpg\n﻿\n換妳試試看：﻿\n記憶中____的味道摸起來____，拿起來____，呈現___，如果它有聲音是____，好像____的畫面。﻿\n﻿\n謝謝收看\n有幫助到妳知道怎麼形容香味的話，可以收藏點愛心讓我知道🥰\n歡迎留言分享妳形容的香味🦋\n———\n艾琳娜香氛秘境","excerpt":"Hello 我是艾琳娜，這是我第一次po文，目前在台灣文創香水公司任職，以後會把大家常見的問題整理成文章分享給你們，如何形容記憶中的味道或是自己想找的香水？你可以想像這5件事～■觸感：柔軟、粗糙、絲綢","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"1a14ba93-3989-47e5-aedc-a3918963100e","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-20T03:25:43.448Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-22T14:35:23.719Z","commentCount":3,"likeCount":25,"tags":[],"topics":["香味","香氛","香水","味道","香氛板"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"香氛","forumAlias":"fragrance","school":"世新大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":25}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/qm9SIcR.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"4589a0f7-70d2-46f6-90a8-2352048a3151","url":"https://i.imgur.com/qm9SIcRl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/qm9SIcRl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/qm9SIcRl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-20T03:25:43.448Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-22T14:35:23.719Z"},{"id":"4589a0f7-70d2-46f6-90a8-2352048a3151","url":"https://i.imgur.com/qm9SIcR.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/qm9SIcR","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/qm9SIcRl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-20T03:25:43.448Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-22T14:35:23.719Z"}],